          "description": "I highly recommend this dentist office! From start to finish, my experience was exceptional. I was looking for a new dentist in Manhattan, and this place truly exceeded my expectations. The staff is not only professional but also friendly and highly skilled. The office itself is beautifully designed, offering a modern, welcoming atmosphere. They go above and beyond to make your visit as comfortable as possible\u2014offering amenities like Beats headphones for music and Gentle Monster sunglasses to enhance the experience during both procedures and check-ups. If you're looking for top-notch care in a relaxing setting, this is the place to go!",
