          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqHH3xXGiUci_bT8SiWHALUYBBsX-QGXWnQTklSO7u7dxjzgoHAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Such a wonderful experience, I would give 10 stars if I could. Dr. Suh and her entire team are kind, patient, and passionate about what they do, and explained every part of the dental exam and cleaning process, which I really appreciate. The interiors are beautiful like a spa, and they give you headphones to listen to music during your cleaning! If that wasn\u2019t enough, for my first visit they gave me a free Philips Sonicare toothbrush, and said every subsequent visit they\u2019ll give me a new head! Such a wonderful experience and I\u2019m so glad I found my new dentist :)",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT213MmFESndjMGt0ZDJWNk1GZHFNWG95YkZSbWFIYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xc7e3b726c28fec00!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmw2aDJwc0ktd2V6MFdqMXoybFRmaHc%7C%7C?hl=en",
