        },
        {
          "username": "Amanda Osei",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "114195042225136605388",
          "user_review_count": 12,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhj6_S1fSl_QgL-Sx7MGYxuk25uZyV355zdrsImdk804slXA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "This was an elevated and unique dental experience with spa like treatment. The moment I walked in, I was greeted with excellent customer service and kindness. Attentive from start to finish. After having a horrible experience at my previous dental office, I was sceptical, however, my hygienist and Dr. Suh made me feel welcome and heard!  Belise, (my hygienist) managed to clean a stain off my composite bonding which I thought wouldn\u2019t have been easy at all. She seamlessly did it in one cleaning session.\n\nThe welcome gift was greatly appreciated, as well as the Netflix/music option whilst cleaning took place. Looking forward to my next visit!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20xRVYxQm9MWFYwZUVGM1UwdE9hbkJ5ZW5kU2FtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xc7e3b726c28fec00!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOm1EV1BoLXV0eEF3U0tOanByendSamc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "2 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-04-17T01:45:19+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Jameson Bui",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "100960899661996963003",
          "user_review_count": 1,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpgDJG7tmhvYi3lW0fBg8Pua6JF2V1b6KGEszLdmCJvXBd8EaX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Hands down the most pleasant dental experience that has ever existed! From the spa-like lobby when you first walk in to the friendly staff, every detail is accounted for. The hygienists are gentle and thorough, the dentists take the time to explain everything clearly, and you can genuinely feel how much they care about your comfort. They even give you headphones to listen to the music of your choice during teeth cleanings. Lucky to have them in the neighborhood. Highly recommend.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WVmRXTXRhbTFaVVc1WE0ySXpialU1YVVwcE1rRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xc7e3b726c28fec00!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOnVVdWMtam1ZUW5XM2IzbjU5aUppMkE%7C%7C?hl=en",
