        },
        {
          "username": "Lisa H",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "112686157315247483120",
          "user_review_count": 15,
          "user_photo_count": 4,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJE5GHU0WEGPgzPGe8yA8lm2ckbMSdkrMjoe8dwmHkazseLbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I had an amazing experience today at Terra! First of all, the venue is very chic and modern, the staff are beautiful and welcoming. As a new patient I had x-rays, hygienist appointment and dental checkup. The service was 5 star, I felt really cared for and special. Everything is spotlessly clean and they had some lovely touches like a tv screen with my name on welcoming me in the check up room. Bose headphones and a remote to select my own choice of music to listen to during treatment. The hygienist was very gentle, usually I dread visits to the hygienist for the pain factor but I experienced no pain. It felt like an afternoon in a spa opposed to the dentist! To top it off I received a welcome gift for being a new patient. I know a lot of people get nervous going to the dentist but if all dentists were like this then people would look forward to their next appointment! Thanks again for a really welcoming visit!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSaVpsa3pWalpQWldOc2VIRlBZV2h3V0VkSU5tYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xc7e3b726c28fec00!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkRiZlkzVjZPZWNseHFPYWhwWEdINmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
