          "description": "This was the best dentist\u2019s visit that I have ever experienced! Previously, I have struggled so much to find a dentist in Manhattan that I like. After one visit to Terra, I know this will be my go-to dentist! Here\u2019s why:\n\n- Dr. Suh is the most professional dentist ever! She takes time to explain everything to you in a very thorough way. You can tell that she is very experienced and has encountered many different types of patients\u2019 dental situations in the past. Also, she suggests only necessary treatments and never pushes anything unnecessary!\n- I was very impressed by the technology they used. For example, they have a machine that takes a 3D scan of your teeth. I haven\u2019t seen that before at other dentists\u2019 offices. That helped me understand what\u2019s going with my teeth and why certain treatments are needed.\n- The office decor is absolutely gorgeous and clean. It feels more like being at a spa than at a dentist\u2019s office.\n- Every aspect of my interaction with Terra- starting with booking my visit to end of the procedure\u2014 was so seamless and pleasant. The staff is also very responsive. There was zero wait when I arrived at my appointment.\n- They paid a lot of attention to small details that make a patient feel welcome and cozy. For example, they give to each patient a dental-related gift to help them keep better dental hygiene. It\u2019s such a nice touch. Also, they have sunglasses and noise cancelling headphones to make your treatment process feel as comfortable as possible.\n- The location is great! It\u2019s easily accessible by train.",
